overview: Private girls go to university for just one reason, there’s only one field that they are interested in and it’s of course the sexual one. Whether it’s a professor, classmate, or just someone passing by, our beauties don’t miss any opportunity to satisfy their sexual appetites as they take the hands on approach to their education and find out what university is really about… sex! Starring Honour May, Lara Lee, Lana Harding, Alexis Crystal and debutant Effie Diaz, a stunning line-up of true Private beauties, with a special shout out to the curvaceous wonder Effie who knows exactly how to raise her grade in an incredible debut, and of course our queen Alexis returns in style with an unforgettable interracial DP threesome. Private Gold, Oxford College Girls, don’ miss it!
title: Oxford College Girls
